{"lexicon" 1, "id" "com.etzhayyim.tadori.traceReport", "description" "Result of a wallet/address trace for a case — the durable, kotoba-persisted output of a malak wallet_deep_inspect_pursuit / address_label_pursuit run (ADR-2605152000), recording the target classification, top counterparties, and aggregated labels as references to tx/addr/cluster/label datoms (ADR-2605301400 §D2). tadori OWNS this durable report; malak owns the ephemeral Pregel super-steps that compute it. G9 Murakumo-only: any LLM verdict in the underlying run routed through the Murakumo gateway (ADR-2605215000). R0 = schema skeleton; R1 = additionalProperties=false.", "defs" {"main" {"type" "record", "key" "tid", "record" {"type" "object", "required" ["createdAt" "caseId" "chain" "targetAddress" "classification" "confidence"], "properties" {"confidence" {"type" "integer", "minimum" 0, "maximum" 1000, "description" "Classification confidence, implied unit per-mille (0..1000 = 0.000..1.000). Integer per Lexicon v1 (no float)."}, "targetAddress" {"type" "string", "description" "The traced address (checksum-valid; ≠ operator self-loop per ADR-2605152000 gate_input)."}, "createdAt" {"type" "string", "format" "datetime", "description" "ISO 8601 UTC timestamp."}, "caseId" {"type" "string", "description" "Owning caseMandate.caseId. G3."}, "runEngine" {"type" "string", "knownValues" ["malak.wallet_deep_inspect_pursuit" "malak.address_label_pursuit"], "description" "The malak Pregel that produced this report."}, "txCount" {"type" "integer", "description" "Total transaction count observed."}, "labelCids" {"type" "array", "items" {"type" "string"}, "description" "CIDs of the label datoms aggregated for this target."}, "externalSourcesUsed" {"type" "array", "items" {"type" "string"}, "description" "G4 OPEN-SOURCE transparency: feature-flagged external data sources consulted (e.g. ofac-sdn / tornado-list / chainalysis-osi). Recorded as INPUTS only; never the system of record."}, "balanceUsd" {"type" "string", "description" "Reported balance (string to avoid float precision loss)."}, "chain" {"type" "string", "description" "Chain id (bsc / eth / btc) — must be in caseMandate.scopeChains."}, "topCounterparties" {"type" "array", "items" {"type" "string"}, "description" "CIDs/IRIs of the top-K counterparty addr datoms (default K=20)."}, "classification" {"type" "string", "knownValues" ["cex_cold" "cex_hot" "dex_router" "bridge_pool" "protocol_pool" "whale_eoa" "mixer" "unknown_eoa" "unverified_contract" "unlabeled_eoa" "sanctioned"], "description" "Wallet classification (ADR-2605152000 output classes). 'bridge_pool' requires explicit bridge-DB or ABI match (v1 false-positive fix)."}}}}}}
